                    </fig>
                  </entry>
                </row>
              </tbody>
            </tgroup>
          </table>
        </p>
        <p>If the array has two or more shelves, connect a
          <uicontrol>QR</uicontrol>
 (6G) or
          <uicontrol>IR</uicontrol>
 (12G) cable pair from
          <uicontrol>CT0</uicontrol>
 to
          <uicontrol>SH1</uicontrol>.
Following are the port numbers:
        </p>
